title: Measure Passes House to Name Bridge in Honor of Local Hero, Delozier Says (RoseMarie Swanger) ...
text: ( Source : RoseMarie Swanger ) HARRISBURG - Legislation to forever acknowledge and remember the sacrifice of a local hero killed in action was passed Monday in the House , said Rep. Sheryl Delozier (R-Cumberland), author of the proposal. House
